data.title: Zelka Energy Solutions, Long Island Energy Management, Long Island Trend Dealer, Long Island Novar Parts Specialist
data.meta_description: Zelka Energy Solutions are Long Island's premier Trend Dealer, Novar Parts specialist, and Energy Management Provider. We offer repairs, retrofits, complete energy solutions, and free energy audits for Long Island.
data.text:
When it comes to Energy management we have built our reputation on simplicity and trust. Beyond the building, behind the systems is the intelligence that unlocks POTENTIAL.

At Zelka Energy we specialize in installation and support of building controls and energy systems. We use leading edge TECHNOLOGY to SIMPLIFY building management for your business, residence, or institution.

We advance with the modern world, creating ENERGY-EFFICIENT buildings and delivering comfortable, economical, secure environments. Our customers TRUST not only in the integrity of our work, but in the strength of our IDEAS.
